  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK613">
<l>tāḷāṇmai yeṉṉun takaimaikkaṭṭaṅkiṟṟē </l>
<l> vēḷāṇmai yeṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lustre of munificence will dwell only with the dignity of laboriousness or efforts.</l>
            </lg>
